<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - Blog Engine</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  
  <main class="container">
    <div class="about-page">
      <h1>About Blog Engine</h1>
      <p>Blog Engine is a full-featured blogging platform built with modern web technologies.</p>
      
      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>User authentication and authorization</li>
        <li>Create, read, update, and delete blog posts</li>
        <li>Markdown support for rich content</li>
        <li>Comments system</li>
        <li>Admin panel for content management</li>
        <li>RESTful API</li>
        <li>Search functionality</li>
        <li>Responsive design</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Node.js & Express.js</li>
        <li>SQLite Database</li>
        <li>Passport.js for Authentication</li>
        <li>EJS Templates</li>
        <li>Marked for Markdown Parsing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
